{"questionId":"10007","questionHtml":"<p>Write down the inverse, <strong><em>A</em></strong><sup>–1</sup>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p style=\"color:#999;font-size:90%;font-style:italic;\">* This question is from an exam for a previous syllabus, and may contain minor differences in marking or structure.</p>\n<p>det <em><strong>A</strong></em> = 5(1)&nbsp;− 7(−2) = 19</p>\n<p><strong><em>A</em></strong><sup>–1</sup>&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = \\frac{1}{{19}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;2 \\\\   { - 7}&amp;5  \\end{array}} \\right) = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\frac{1}{{19}}}&amp;{\\frac{2}{{19}}} \\\\   {\\frac{{ - 7}}{{19}}}&amp;{\\frac{5}{{19}}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>19</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>19</mn>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>19</mn>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mn>7</mn>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>19</mn>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>19</mn>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(A2)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Award <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em> for&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;2 \\\\   { - 7}&amp;5  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em> for dividing by 19.</p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><strong><em>A</em></strong><sup>–1</sup>&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {0.0526}&amp;{0.105} \\\\   { - 0.368}&amp;{0.263}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>0.0526